# Boot Sonic 2, do not press Start. Let title screen demo timer
# expire (~10s + 40 frames after title screen reaches steady state)
# and capture state at the attract demo entry / freeze point.
#
# Sonic 2's attract demo path goes:
#   SEGA logo ($00) -> Title screen ($04) -> TitleCard|Demo ($88) -> Demo ($08)
#
# The user reports a black-screen freeze on attract entry. This
# script gives the game ample time to reach demo and dumps state.

WAIT_RAM8 FFF600 04
# Title screen reached. Demo_Time_left initialized to 640 (10.7s).
WAIT 800
# By here we should be in TitleCard|Demo ($88) or Demo ($08).
DUMP_RAM attract_freeze_t1_ram.bin
SCREENSHOT attract_freeze_t1.png

WAIT 600
# 10 more seconds past first state capture.
DUMP_RAM attract_freeze_t2_ram.bin
SCREENSHOT attract_freeze_t2.png

WAIT 600
DUMP_RAM attract_freeze_t3_ram.bin
SCREENSHOT attract_freeze_t3.png

EXIT 0
